The All Progressives Congress (APC) National leader o Bola Tinubu has revealed what he would do if he loses the party’s primaries. In a video shared by Jubril Gawat, a media aide to Governor Babajide Sanwo-Olu, on Twitter, Tinubu who spoke in the Yoruba language assured his followers that he would win but If he does not, he will accept defeat. Watch video below -Advertisement-